import { Stack, TextField} from '@mui/material'

const MuiTextField = () => {
  return (
    <Stack spacing={4}>
        <Stack direction='row' spacing={2}>
        <TextField label='Name'variant='outlined'/>
        <TextField 
        label='Filled' 
        variant='filled'
        size='small' 
        color='secondary'
        required
        />
        <TextField label='Standard' variant='standard'/>

        </Stack>
    </Stack>

  )
}

export default MuiTextField
